        <abstract> 
<p>Sends CD a quotation from Plato which anticipates the <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p>  
<p>Has been enjoying CD’s paper on dimorphism in the <hi rend="italic">Journal of the Linnean Society</hi> ["Two forms of <hi rend="italic">Primula</hi>", <hi rend="italic">Collected papers</hi> 2: 45–63]. He has found similar structures [see <hi rend="italic">Forms of flowers</hi>, pp. 116, 122].</p> 
        </abstract>
